  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides extension methods to work with string normalization.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[

## Remarks

The extension methods of the <xref:System.StringNormalizationExtensions> class are designed to work with .NET implementations that do not support the <xref:System.String.IsNormalized*?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.String.Normalize*?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods. However, these methods are included in the <xref:System.String> class in .NET Standard 2.0 and are therefore available on all .NET implementations that support the .NET Standard 2.0. For more information, see [.NET Standard](/dotnet/standard/net-standard).

        ]]></format>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
